OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778094687
OL,3,CPolice attacked at car meet in west
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,FTwo PSNI officers and several police
OL,7,Fvehicles have been attacked at a car
OL,8,Fmeet in west Belfast.
OL,10,FFootage on social media showed cars
OL,11,Fdriving erratically with crowds of
OL,12,Fpeople gathered in the Colin area on
OL,13,FMonday evening.
OL,15,FPolice received reports of large
OL,16,Fcrowds of people and vehicles that
OL,17,Fgathered and were driving dangerously
OL,18,Fin the vicinity of Blacks Road and
OL,19,FBell Steele Road.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
