OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778094687
OL,3,CPolice attacked at car meet in west
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Officers
OL,7,Fattended and subsequently came under
OL,8,Fattack by youths throwing bottles and
OL,9,Fmasonry.
OL,11,F"Two officers were struck and number
OL,12,Fof police vehicles were damaged in the
OL,13,Fattack.
OL,15,F"I would appeal to those people
OL,16,Finvolved in this kind of reckless
OL,17,Fbehaviour on our roads to think about
OL,18,Fthe possible serious consequence of
OL,19,Ftheir actions.
OL,26,@nD@[OUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778094687
OL,3,CPolice attacked at car meet in west
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,F"Not only does this kind of activity
OL,7,Fimpact on the lives of local
OL,8,Fresidents, but it can present a
OL,9,Fsignificant danger to other road users.
OL,11,F"I would also urge those involved to
OL,12,Fbe aware that police will use all
OL,13,Fpowers available to them to ensure the
OL,14,Fsafety of road users, including the
OL,15,Fpower to seize vehicles.
OL,17,F"We have been, and will continue to
OL,18,Fwork with our partner organisations,
OL,19,Fincluding local politicians, to
OL,20,Faddress this issue, and work towards
OL,21,Fdelivering a safe solution.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778094687
OL,3,CPolice attacked at car meet in west
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,F"An evidence-gathering operation was
OL,7,Fin place and an investigation is now
OL,8,Funder way to identify those involved
OL,9,Fin disorder."
OL,11,FSinn Fein MLA Danny Baker condemned
OL,12,Fthose involved in scenes he described
OL,13,Fas "absolutely chaotic and nothing
OL,14,Fshort of a disgrace".
OL,16,FHe also criticised the PSNI who he
OL,17,Fclaimed did not arrive "until the
OL,18,Fsituation had already got out of
OL,19,Fcontrol".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@MO]uD@DOUvD@TO]yD@XOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778094687
OL,3,CPolice attacked at car meet in west
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,F"Police were made aware several hours
OL,7,Fago of this pre-planned event and I
OL,8,Furged them to deploy preventative
OL,9,Fmeasures to stop the cavalcade of cars
OL,10,Ffrom entering the area," he said.
OL,12,F"These concerns fell on deaf ears, and
OL,13,Fby the time police arrived it was too
OL,14,Flate.
OL,16,F"I will be requesting an urgent
OL,17,Fmeeting with police to reflect the
OL,18,Ffeelings of people in the Colin who
OL,19,Ffeel completely let down.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]tD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778094687
OL,3,CPolice attacked at car meet in west
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,F"I am also urging swift action to
OL,7,Fensure those involved in this reckless
OL,8,Fbehaviour are apprehended."
OL,10,FIndependent Councillor for West
OL,11,FBelfast Paul Doherty posted on social
OL,12,Fmedia: "If any of your young people
OL,13,Fare out around the Stewartstown Road
OL,14,Ftonight, get them home now.
OL,16,F"This is disgraceful, dangerous and
OL,17,Ftotally unacceptable. People are
OL,18,Fputting lives at risk and terrorising
OL,19,Fthe local community.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@[O]tD@HOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1778094687
OL,3,CPolice attacked at car meet in west
OL,4,CBelfast
OL,6,F"Parents and guardians need to know
OL,7,Fwhere their young people are. Get them
OL,8,Faway from this before someone is
OL,9,Fkilled."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]
